textBody:
Furry may refer to:

* Furry, the quality of being made of or covered in fur
* Furry, a member of the furry fandom

People

* Wendell H. Furry (1907–1984), professor of physics
* Furry Lewis (1893 or 1899–1981), American country blues guitarist and songwriter
